    <div class='jumbotron text-center' style='color: maroon'>
      <h3>Door Bell Slack Bot</h3>
      <p>
        This bot has been implemented into the SDCS slack workspace to improve the student experience.
      </p>
      <a class='float-left' href='/projects' style='color: maroon'>
